      "wikitext": "{{Infobox animal\n|image      = Dinosaur.png\n|building   = {{Name|Big Coop}}\n|produce    = {{Name|Dinosaur Egg}}\n}}\nThe '''Dinosaur''' is a farm [[Animals|animal]] that lives in a [[Coop|Big Coop]]. Dinosaurs can be hatched by placing a [[Dinosaur Egg]] into an [[Incubator]], taking {{duration|18,000m (11d 6h 40m)|class=inline}} to incubate, or {{duration|9,000m (5d 16h 40m)|class=inline}} with the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Coopmaster Profession]]. \n\n==Produce==\n{{main article|Animals#Produce}}\nDinosaurs are born mature. A mature and fed dinosaur produces a [[Dinosaur Egg]] every 7 days, which can be placed in an [[Incubator]] to hatch another dinosaur, or sold for {{Price|350}}. If you have used the [[File:Treasure Appraisal Guide.png|24px]] [[Treasure Appraisal Guide]] the egg instead sells for {{Price|1050}}.\n\nA Dinosaur Egg can be placed in a [[Mayonnaise Machine]] to produce [[Dinosaur Mayonnaise]], which sells for {{Price|800}}.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Sell Price\n|-\n|[[File:Dinosaur Egg.png]]\n|[[Dinosaur Egg]]\n|{{Description|Dinosaur Egg}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Dinosaur Egg|350|dsv=false}}\n|}\n\n==Selling==\nIt is possible to sell the Dinosaur. A Dinosaur with more hearts sells for more [[gold]]. A Dinosaur with maximum hearts sells for {{Price|1300}}. A dinosaur with no hearts sells for {{Price|315}}.\n\n''Note that a dinosaur with 0 hearts of friendship technically sells for {{Price|300}}, but the player cannot access the 'sell' menu without petting the dinosaur, which gives 15 friendship points (30 with the [[Skills#Farming|Coopmaster]] profession), and increases the sell price to {{Price|315}} ({{Price|330}} with Coopmaster).''\n\nTo sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much the animal can be sold for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n\n==Trivia==\n* If you talk to [[Demetrius]] after hatching a dinosaur, he will get excited about it. So excited that he can't finish his {{Name|Triple Shot Espresso|class=inline}}, which he gives to the farmer instead.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.2.26|Fixed bug where they wouldn't produce [[Animals#Produce|goods]] at high happiness.}}\n{{History|1.4|Fixed bug allowing wallpaper #108 to be placed in an incubator in lieu of a Dinosaur Egg.}}\n{{History|1.6|A new dialogue interaction was added with [[Demetrius]] for hatching a dinosaur. Additionally, a new [[Books|book of power]] interaction increases the value of unprocessed dinosaur eggs.}}\n\n{{NavboxAnimals}}\n\n[[Category:Coop animals]]\n\n[[de:Dinosaurier]]\n[[es:Dinosaurio]]\n[[fr:Dinosaure]]\n[[it:Dinosauro]]\n[[ja:恐竜]]\n[[ko:공룡]]\n[[hu:Dinoszaurusz]]\n[[pt:Dinossauro]]\n[[ru:Динозавр]]\n[[tr:Dinozor]]\n[[zh:恐龙]]"
